											<span id="DataList1__ctl7_Label1"><font face="Verdana" size="1"><P>I just deployed a patch that allows you to register a custom domain (<A href="http://www.yourguild.com">www.yourguild.com</A>), and use it instead of the semi-private guildwizard (<A href="http://yourguild.guildwizard.com">http://yourguild.guildwizard.com</A>) address.&nbsp; You can click the `Domains` button for more details, there is a FAQ link there too for more details.&nbsp; </P>
<P>If you already have a domain registered, and would like to use it, it can be used as well.&nbsp; You have to point your DNS to our server and inform us of your intention to do so, so that we can add your domain to our accepted domain list.&nbsp; </P>
<P>Next patch will take care of the issues that have been reported in the last couple weeks.&nbsp; Raid, Encounter, Item grid sorting is up first.. I am also going to do some searching in certain areas where the cache isn`t updating immediatly, namely after raids are entered.</P></font></span>
